package tools.maran.svg.materialdesign;

import tools.maran.svg.SVG;

/// Material Design Icons representing **abstract UI concepts and interface elements**.
/// Contains all Interface SVG paths, which can be retrieved by calling {@link #path()} or {@link #toString()}.
///
/// This category groups everything used to build, control, and annotate user interfaces:
///
/// - **Charts & Data Viz** — graphs, polls, timelines, progress indicators
/// - **UI Controls** — checkboxes, toggles, buttons, tooltips, cursors, widgets
/// - **Actions** — CRUD operations, clipboard actions, undo/redo, sharing
/// - **Playback Controls** — play, pause, stop, skip, rewind, record
/// - **Navigation** — arrows, chevrons, menus, tabs, breadcrumbs
/// - **Layout & Visual Design** — grids, layers, alignment, cropping, color palettes
/// - **Shapes** — circles, stars, hexagons, cubes, hearts, abstract geometry
/// - **Time** — clocks, calendars, timers
/// - **Security & Settings** — locks, keys, shields, fingerprints, cogs
/// - **Text & Window Management** — text boxes, window controls, aspect ratios, drag handles
/// - **Notifications** — bells, alerts, badges, party poppers
/// - **Accounts** — profiles, login/logout, badges
/// - **Alphanumeric & Math** — Greek letters, operators, number systems, formulas
/// - **Symbols & Punctuation** — copyright, trademark, logic gates, sizing indicators, default emoticons, thumbs up
///
